sequenceDiagram
    participant User1 as Nutzer 1
    participant User2 as Nutzer 2
    participant User3 as Nutzer 3
    participant System as System

    User1->>System: Initiate group call
    System-->>User1: Confirm call setup
    User2->>System: Join group call
    System-->>User2: Confirm joined
    User3->>System: Join group call
    System-->>User3: Confirm joined
    System-->>User1: Notify participants joined
    System-->>User2: Notify participants joined
    System-->>User3: Notify participants joined
    User1->>System: Start video/audio stream
    System-->>User1: Stream started
    User2->>System: Start video/audio stream
    System-->>User2: Stream started
    User3->>System: Start video/audio stream
    System-->>User3: Stream started